% bayes-hdc — canonical bibliography
% =================================
%
% This file is the single source of truth for the canonical citations
% used throughout the codebase. Every primary HDC/VSA paper that the
% library cites in a docstring, design note, or example points back to
% one of the entries below by BibTeX key. The keys follow the
% lastname-year-shortword convention so they are stable across renames.
%
% The literature audit at docs/LITERATURE_AUDIT.md ties each paper to
% the specific file:line locations where it is cited and records the
% recommended canonical citation form. If you add a new citation,
% extend this file and reference it from the docstring rather than
% inlining the BibTeX inside the source.

